---
title: Homestyle Crumbed Chicken & Apple Slaw with Lemony Crushed Potatoes
description: Chicken, potatoes and slaw - the classic combo that proves simple pleasures always win. We’ve thrown in a few flavour bombs to amp things up; our smokey All-American seasoning in the crumb, a lemony twist on the hot crushed potatoes, and refreshing and sweet apple mixed through the slaw.
